52 Sanidassanattika, Sappaccayaduka
Sanidassanattika, Sappaccayaduka
95.
235Anidassanaappaṭigho appaccayo dhammo nasanidassanasappaṭighassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
236Ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā tīṇi, upanissaye tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
